{
  "stem": "15017.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there comes a time-- she was 11 years old-- a girl's got to be ready for anything that happens physically.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'47.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was-- so I arranged it with the, with the, with BOAC at that time that she leave London under the stewardess' supervision, and she would arrive the same day as the ship got into New York, with my fingers crossed that the ship was going to arrive on time.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because sometimes with the bad weather, even though we arrived late, we sailed on time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ship arrived on time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "God [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunt and uncle were waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And straight away, they drove us over to LaGuardia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, LaGuardia was the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--international airport.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm up on the balcony, watching the people coming in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as my daughter comes in on the hand of the stewardess, I give her the whistle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, that's my daddy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's my daddy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I ran down quickly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to sign, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The stewardess gave me to her, introduced her to her uncle and aunt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had something to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to see the [NON-ENGLISH], which was my mother's sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you know-- and then they went up to Massachusetts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And every time I used to get into port we used to-- if I got into port and we were in for more than a day and a half or two and a half, I used to take the train from Penn Central Station.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I used to take the train to Great Barrington in Massachusetts to see her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she did very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She went to college in Boston.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there, she met a young man who was a pharmacist, a chemist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they fell in love with each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
